author: tomj
msg: - Correctly support username/password protected WSDL files in Emitter.
XMLUtils.newDocument now takes a username and password, if they are
set and we are using the http or https protocol, we go and fetch the document
ourselves so we can provide the HTTP Basic Authentication header
- Set the global Authenticator only if WSDL2Java is invoked from the
command line.  Since this is a global setting, programs that embed Axis
would be hosed if they used this mechanism.
Do not try and open the URL, this will fail with a password
protected URL and later code will fail if the URL is missing.
